												<div class="description author withsidebar">
													<h6><a href="https://lithub.com/author/annesomerset/">Anne Somerset</a></h6>
													Anne Somerset was born in London and graduated from King’s College, London. She is the author of <em>The Life and Times of King William IV</em>, <em>Ladies in Waiting</em>, <em>Elizabeth I</em>, <em>Queen Anne</em>, and <em>Queen Victoria and Her Prime Ministers</em>. She has worked as a research assistant for several historians, among them Antonia Fraser. Somerset is the daughter of the 11th Duke of Beaufort. She lives in London.																									</div>
											</div><br class="clear"/><br/>
										</div>

